HEADWORD: parapsychological
<hw>parapsychological</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
parapsychology; pertaining to forces or mental processes outside the
possibilities defined by natural or scientific laws; <as>as,
<ex>parapsychological</ex> research</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> psychic, psychical, parapsycholological,
paranormal.</syn>⟦br⟧
